title: Fortios: Interface
agents: special
catalog: network/fortigate
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the Interfaces of a Fortigate firewall.
 All interfaces are monitored by default, provided that 
 no discovery rule has been configured.
 This check supports multiple Fortigate VDOMs.


 The special agent is required for this check, 
 which can be configured via “FortiOS”.

discovery:
 One service per interface is created.
 The discovery of interfaces can be configured.
 The "discovery_fortios_interface" rule can be used to configure the 
 detection of interfaces using regex.
 It is also possible to recognize the interfaces by description, 
 name or alias.
